The paper focuses on an image classification task using deep learning models, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the impact of data ordering on model performance, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses metrics such as NDCG, which is commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
